name: Washington Redskins Miniature Back Pack
description:
Washington Redskins NFL miniature back pack, NEW

Burgundy and black with NFL chain emblem will go over well with the youngsters and you may find grown-ups like this miniature back pack too. 

Padded straps for ease on your back, side mesh pockets for accessories or drink, two zippers open from top, and top handle with easy holding. 

Mesh pocket on one back padded strap and solid pocket on the other strap! Lots of room!

This would make a great gift for birthdays or that Redskins fanatic. 

Use it for quick trips, school, to the games, pack kid-stuff, just about anything you need a bag for!
 
 FREE Redskin Tissue Holder with each purchase!
